</p>
</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA12d193n1-ptr" id="PJA12d193n1">1</a>
<p>The passage from this point through le 3e. May was written in the left margin and marked for insertion at this point.</p>
</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA12d193n2-ptr" id="PJA12d193n2">2</a>
